dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Piedras Blancas and San Simeon quadrangles, San Luis Obispo County, California
dct_alternative_sm: Piedras Blancas and San Simeon map
Geology Piedras Blancas and San Simeon quadrangles
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.

"Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle Piedras Blancas CA 1959. Photoinspected 1980. DMA 1755 III NE - Series V895. San Simeon CA 1958. Photoinspected 1976. DMA 1755 II NW - Series V895."
Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology, most recent 1975.
